## Verification Plan

### Browser Testing
1. Run `cd frontend && npm run dev -- --host` (already running)
2. Open the app in the browser
3. Verify the **sun/moon toggle** switches between light and dark mode instantly
4. Open the **palette dropdown** and click each theme — verify colors change across all sections (header, search, cards, procedure list)
5. Refresh the page — verify the chosen theme persists
6. Test dropdown closes when clicking outside
